            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hi,</p><p>My name is Albert.</p><p>Today I have started developing a project called <strong>Free Kalmykia in Numbers</strong>. I am welcoming everyone who are interested in economics and politics to join me in the efforts to answer a question: "Is Independent Kalmykia viable?".</p><p><img loading="lazy" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9f/Flag_of_Kalmykia.svg" alt="Docusaurus Plushie" class="img_ev3q"></p>]]></content:encoded>
